<!--
  PRESERVED EXAMPLE — a known-good working mandate: the high-risk volatile-US-stocks
  trend-following brief this system ran under during large-model research sessions.
  No selector ever loads a .example file (the loader reads MANDATE.md, profiles/<name>.md,
